snippet.title: Bakra Nahi Majnu Halaal - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Duolingo and learn any language for free - https://app.adjust.net.in/jgl36j4

Ye life achche achchon ko halaal kar deti hain lekin hamare Rinku ki kahani thodi different hain. Isne khud ja ke musibat se panga liya. Rinku ki life mast chal rahi thi. Bade sheher mein sarkari naukari ki tayyari kar raha tha aur ek girlfriend bhi thi, Raveena, jo isse apna naukar samajhti thi Par phir bhi Rinku apne roommate Neetu ke sath khush tha. Phir iski life mein aayi Sangeeta aur life mein 5th gear lag gaya. Ek ke baad ek kamaal hone laga aur apna Rinku halaal hone laga. Yakeen na ho to khud dekh lo. Ek aisi kahani jis mein music hai, drama hai, action hai ( Rinku ki life mein ) , romance hai aur bahut saari confusion ke sath double dose of comedy bhi hai. Full family ke sath enjoy this special presentation

snippet.title: Maha Episode 💥 | Current Affairs 2022 January to December | Kumar Gaurav Sir | Utkarsh Classes
snippet.description:
#currentaffairs2022 #currentaffairsrevision #kumargauravsir 

Maha Episode 💥 | Current Affairs 2022 January to December | Kumar Gaurav Sir | Utkarsh Classes 

📢"महा एपिसोड🔥 वार्षिकांक लॉन्च" 
2022 के करेंट अफेयर्स का सूपड़ा साफ़।
जी हाँ, नव वर्ष के प्रथम दिन को पढ़ाई के नजरिए से यादगार बनाने के लिए कुमार सर अपने प्यारे शेर, शेरनियों के लिए 2022 के करेंट अफेयर्स का एक ही क्लास में सूपड़ा साफ़ करने के लिए पूरे जोश और जुनून के साथ ले रहें हैं और “करेंट अफेयर्स वार्षिकांक-2022” की विशेष सौगात भी साथ 3 यानी नए साल के पहले ही दिन खुशियों का डबल डोज।
तो, 1 Jan 2023 की शाम को 7 बजे जुड़ने से बिल्कुल भी चूकिएगा मत, क्योंकि इस क्लास के माध्यम से 2022 का सम्पूर्ण करेंट अफेयर्स होने वाला है आपकी मुट्ठी में।

#currentaffairs2022 #currentaffairsrevision #kumargauravsir 

Maha Episode 💥 | Current Affairs 2022 January to December | Kumar Gaurav Sir | Utkarsh Classes 

📢"महा एपिसोड🔥 वार्षिकांक लॉन्च" 
2022 के करेंट अफेयर्स का सूपड़ा साफ़।
जी हाँ, नव वर्ष के प्रथम दिन को पढ़ाई के नजरिए से यादगार बनाने के लिए कुमार सर अपने प्यारे शेर, शेरनियों के लिए 2022 के करेंट अफेयर्स का एक ही क्लास में सूपड़ा साफ़ करने के लिए पूरे जोश और जुनून के साथ ले रहें हैं और “करेंट अफेयर्स वार्षिकांक-2022” की विशेष सौगात भी साथ 3 यानी नए साल के पहले ही दिन खुशियों का डबल डोज।
तो, 1 Jan 2023 की शाम को 7 बजे जुड़ने से बिल्कुल भी चूकिएगा मत, क्योंकि इस क्लास के माध्यम से 2022 का सम्पूर्ण करेंट अफेयर्स होने वाला है आपकी मुट्ठी में।

snippet.title: Every Indian Wedding Ever | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys
This Video shows all the crazy fun that happens in Big Fat Indian weddings. Relatives giving advices about marriage. All the money , gifts , wedding preps , indian food , gol gappe , tikki , chart items , Paneer Tikka ,  spicy food , indian sweets , shaadi lehenga , bride makeup , wedding shopping , crazy dancing on wedding songs . Indian aunties taking lime light . Mehendi functions getting henna done and celebrating with family , friends , cousins . Ldki Wale vs ladke Wale , wedding photographers , pharo time and shadi wali coffee and crying on bidai , attending Big Fat Indian weddings like Kohli Tents , Flying Drones in weddings , Grand , Indian Bride entry with russians arounds , Wide variety of Indian Wedding Tasty food , malai chaap to gulab jamun , jalebi rabri , ice cream , Kids wearing skivi sweater under lehenga to deal with winter weddings , the struggles of Rishta before Marraige , Dealing with dowry , Every Girls struugles , Indian mom and super excited for daughter wedding , dreaming about grandchidlren , her beti being a maa one day , buying and placing a lot indian snacks daal kachori , samosa , pakore , dry fruits & nuts , barati ready for baraat dance on dhol , tired from 7 days of shadi functions , haldi , cocktail , sangeet , god tikka , mehendi , god bharai , halwai at home , indian relatives and theri demands , exclusive parlour makeup , hd bridal makeup , celebrity makeup , airbrush makeup , glitter makeup , high wedding makeup and hairstyle prices , wonder ladies with babies in wedding and doing rasams , dealing traffic jam while reaching a shaadi , every girls efforts of getting in lehenga , jhumka , doing makeup and then getting out of lehenga , removing heavy layers of makeup before sleeping , removing jwelery bangles , high heels , going on honeymoon and celebrating New Year goa , newyork , paris , london , switerland , enjoying bhaji , mathi achar , bondi ladoo , with tea or masala Chai , Going to Chandi Chowk for bridal shopping , choosing from wide variety of Bride lehenga color choices , red , maroon , pink , blue , green , trying different designs sabyasachi , manish malhotra , celebrity bridal lehengas , lehenga from jaipur with heavy embroidery work , crazy lehenga shopkeppers , high prices of lehenga and bargaining in that , bride not able to diet near marraige eating outside food golgappe to curb with full day of wedding shopping , after wedding counting money got from shagun , decorating gold daimond jewelry in front of indian guest buidling new homes before marraige , saas bahu happy in their new mother daughter relationship , kids mesmerized by new bhabhi and her makeup kit . 
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in an indian wedding.  
Relish and Relive your Memories.. You will have major nostalgia .
Do share it with your friends , family , Relatives and Cousins .. A Very Happy New Year Guys 
Comment down your Fav Part, 
Like, Share and 
Subscribe to our Channel - http://bit.ly/thepaayaljain | Press Bell Icon

Follow Us On Instagram : 
Paayal Jain : https://www.instagram.com/thepaayalja...
Tena Jaiin : https://www.instagram.com/tenajaiin/?...

Cast :
Paayal Jain , Tena Jaiin , Vineet Tripathi 

Script , Direction , Screenplay By : Paayal Jain , Tena Jaiin
Dop : Imran Khan
Cam Assist : Farid Ahmad
Editor : Sahil Arora
Thumbnail by : Shanu Jannat
Shop Location : Fab Creations , Jwala Heri

snippet.title: Women Task Force | The Coffin Man Is After Officer Purvi's Life | CID | Full Episode | 01.01.2023
snippet.description:
A criminal has been sentenced to some years in jail for his crimes. During this time, his daughter has an accident and ends up losing her life. He visits her to identify the body but ends up losing his life too. The authorities handed over the case to Team CID. How will they solve this mystery? Watch the full episode to find out! 

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1480
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #livcrime #सीआईडी 

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: पुत्रदा एकादशी की कथा || putrada ekadashi vrat katha || ekadashi vrat katha
snippet.description:
पुत्रदा एकादशी की कथा || putrada ekadashi vrat katha || ekadashi vrat katha
पौष शुक्ल एकादशी का नाम पुत्रदा एकादशी है। यह सब पापों को हरने वाली उत्तम तिथि है। इसमें समस्त कामनाओं तथा सिद्धियोंके दाता नारायण भगवान की पूजा की जाती है। इस चर और अचर संसार में पुत्रदा एकादशी के व्रत के समान दूसरा कोई व्रत नहीं है। इसके पुण्य से मनुष्य तपस्वी, विद्वान और लक्ष्मीवान होता है।  पुत्रदा एकादशी का  व्रत करने वाले मनुष्य को सुबह उठकर स्नान करना चाहिए। अगर आप संतान प्राप्ति के लिए व्रत कर रहे हैं तो पति पत्नी दोनों को इसका व्रत करना चाहिए। स्नान के पश्चात पूरे विधि विधान से भगवान विष्णु की पूजा करें। आप चाहें तो भगवान विष्णु या कृष्ण के मंदिर जाकर वहां पूजा करें और प्रसाद चढ़ाएं। भगवान विष्णु की आरती करें। इस व्रत में रात्रि जागरण का विशेष महत्व है।
इसकी मैं एक कथा कहता हूँ सो तुम ध्यानपूर्वक सुनो।

Pausha Shukla Ekadashi Ekadashi is named Putrada Ekadashi. This is the best date to defeat all sins. In this, the Lord Narayana, the giver of all desires and siddhis, is worshiped. There is no other fast in this variable and constant world like Putrada Ekadashi fast. By its virtue, a man is an ascetic, scholar and Lakshmivan. A person fasting for Putrada Ekadashi should wake up in the morning and take a bath. If you are fasting to get children, then both husband and wife should observe this fast. After bathing, worship Lord Vishnu with full legal practice. If you want, go to the temple of Lord Vishnu or Krishna and worship there and make offerings. Perform aarti of Lord Vishnu. Night awakening has special significance in this fast.
I tell a story about it, so listen carefully.
 #putradaekadashi #paushshuklaekadashikatha  #पुत्रदा_एकादशी  #एकादशी

snippet.description:
नहीं रहीं हीरा बा..पीएम मोदी की मां हीरा बा..जिनका जिक्र अक्सर सोशल मीडिया से लेकर सियासी गलियारों में होता था..जिनके साथ की पीएम मोदी झट से पलक झपकते वायरल हो जातीं..आज भी हैं लेकिन शोक संदेश के साथ..कि नहीं रहीं हीरा बा..100 साल की उम्र में पीएम मोदी की मां हीरा बा ने दुनिया को अलविदा कर दिया..जिसकी जानकारी खुद पीएम मोदी ने दो बड़े ही भावुक संदेश के साथ दी..कुछ ऐसा ही दर्द सीएम योगी ने भी बयां किया..मायावती ने भी श्रद्धांजलि

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 01 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - 28th December 2022 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 01 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - 28th December 2022 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Gokuldham में चल रही है Special Party | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah |Sony Sab Rewind
snippet.description:
Jethalal and his friends return to the Gokuldham Society from the police station. Tappu Sena arranges breakfast for their parents. But is another mess awaiting them? Watch the full episode to find out! 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast – Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode No – 2188
Produced By – Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #SAB #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा  

Click here to subscribe to Sony SAB Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son, he calls his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Click here to enjoy some of the most cherished episodes from 'Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah':
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7aEDVX8XJrhP79i2DeWf6gm

snippet.title: Roar of Veera Simha Reddy - The Making Video | Nandamuri Balakrishna | Gopichand Malineni | Thaman S
snippet.description:
Roar of Veera Simha Reddy - The Making Video on Mythri Movie Makers. Presenting our NATASIMHAM Nandamuri Balakrishna, Shruti Haasan and Varalaxmi Sarathkumar in Veera Simha Reddy. The film has been Written and Directed by Gopichand Malineni. Music composed by Thaman S. Cinematography helmed by Rishi Punjabi. Dialogues Penned by Sai Madhav Burra and Editing by Navin Nooli. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y Ravi Shankar, under the banner Mythri Movie Makers.

Veera SimhaReddy Grand Release on 12th January, 2023.

#VeeraSimhaReddy #NatasimhamNandamuriBalakrishna #ShrutiHaasan #GopichandMalineni #VaralaxmiSarathkumar #HoneyRose #SaiMadhavBurra #ThamanS

Lyrics (Hindi )

नया साल तो मनाएंगे हम खाटू धाम पे जकार
बाबा हैप्पी न्यू ईयर कर भक्तों पे मेहर

सबसे पहले तुम्हें बधाई तू है सबसे प्यारा
सपने सारे पूरे करना देना साथ हमारा
साल नया ये खुशियां लाए हो पिछले से बेहतर
बाबा हैप्पी न्यू ईयर कर भक्तों पे मेहर

छोटे से मेरे मन में आशाएं अपार है
होंगी पूरी तेरी कृपा से मुझको एतबार है
धन्य करो हे खाटूवाले चरनो में बिठाकर
बाबा हैप्पी न्यू ईयर कर भक्तों पे मेहर

सालों साल बीत  गए अटूट अपना नाता है
हर सुख दुख में बाबा श्याम ही याद मुझे तो आता है
सुकून बड़ा मिलता है प्रभु तेरे दर पे आकर
बाबा हैप्पी न्यू ईयर कर भक्तों पे मेहर

Lyrics (English)

Naya Saal To  Manayenge Hum Khatu Dhaam Pe Jakar
Baba Happy New Year Kar Bhakton Pe Meher

Sabse Pehle Tumhe Badhaai Tu  Hai Sabse Pyaara 
Sapne Saare Poore Karna Dena Saath Hamara 
Saal Naya Ye Khushiyan Laaye Ho Pichle Se Behtar

Chhote Se Mere Man Mein Aashayen Apaar Hai
Hongi Poori Teri Kripa Se Mujhko Aetbaar Hai
Dhanya Karo He Khatuwale Charno Mein Bithakar

Saalon Saal Beet Gaye Atoot Apna Naata Hai
Har Sukh Dukh Mein Baba Shyam Hi Yaad Mujhe To Aata Hai
Sukoon Bada Milta Hai Prabhu Tere Dar Pe Aakar

snippet.title: Bihaan हुआ गिरफ़्तार! | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 579
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

In his pursuit to save Thapki, Bihaan accidentally pushes Sankar off the cliff. The police arrest Bihaan for Sankar's murder. Is Sankar really dead or is this just a part of another vicious plan?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: Women Task Force | Purvi's Bravery Saves The Life Of CID Officers | CID | Full Episode | 31.12.2022
snippet.description:
The CID team enters the bungalow where a notorious hacker is hiding. They find a secret passageway that leads to the hacker's hideout. At the end of the passage, they find the hacker pointing a gun at them. The CID succeeds in narrowing down the threat and arresting the hacker. But, this is only the beginning as the arrest leads the CID team into the trap of a sinister criminal. Watch the entire episode to get your answer. 

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1475
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #livcrime #सीआईडी 

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

Click here to watch more clips:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0y08jtgaKIW-oBRmsADGpsfuNkU81C

snippet.title: After 8 Years Of Making Content...
snippet.description:
Check out my Meditation app: Level SuperMind
Android: https://lvl.fit/android30/12
ios: https://lvl.fit/ios30/12

Join the Level Community Here:
https://linktr.ee/levelsupermindcommunity

A humble request to you in this one.
Starting with a story - I was deeply depressed at the start of 2022. I'd moved into my dream house, but without my family. As more wealth entered my life, it made me feel less challenged. And for the warrior in me, a challenge less life felt almost empty. It took a LOT of self-work to actually enjoy life again.

I'd worked throughout my 20s towards this very dream. Stable businesses, a loving team, and lots of material success. The world tells you all your life that money, fame, and even love are life's goals. But trust me, my friend, even after getting all 3, there will be countless moments when you feel empty. To the point where I wanted to quit YouTube, social media, business, and everything in between.

What rescued me finally was therapy and meditation. I recommend the combination highly to ANYONE that feels any sort of "lack" in life. Even healed people need therapy. I'm not a professional therapist.

But I am an entrepreneur. And what I can recommend with all my heart is the meditation app we've been building out for the last 2 years.

Learnt, relearnt, and now SHARING this lesson 🙏🏻

I hope my story gives YOU hope.
Level Supermind is live in the App Store & play store. Download the free trial now!

A humble request to you in this one.
Starting with a story - I was deeply depressed at the start of 2022. I'd moved into my dream house, but without my family. As more wealth entered my life, it made me feel less challenged. And for the warrior in me, a challenge less life felt almost empty. It took a LOT of self-work to actually enjoy life again.

I'd worked throughout my 20s towards this very dream. Stable businesses, a loving team, and lots of material success. The world tells you all your life that money, fame, and even love are life's goals. But trust me, my friend, even after getting all 3, there will be countless moments when you feel empty. To the point where I wanted to quit YouTube, social media, business, and everything in between.

What rescued me finally was therapy and meditation. I recommend the combination highly to ANYONE that feels any sort of "lack" in life. Even healed people need therapy. I'm not a professional therapist.

But I am an entrepreneur. And what I can recommend with all my heart is the meditation app we've been building out for the last 2 years.

Learnt, relearnt, and now SHARING this lesson 🙏🏻

I hope my story gives YOU hope.
Level Supermind is live in the App Store & play store. Download the free trial now!

snippet.title: Clash of Clans - 2022 Year in Review
snippet.description:
Welcome to our Museum of 2022 - a humble look back on everything that has happened in Clash of Clans over the course of this year. From our most ambitious update, Clan Capital, to Town Hall 15 - the largest Town Hall update we've ever made, 2022 shaped up to be one of the biggest and most exciting years for Clashers ever. Not only did we see new Troops, new Defenses, new Hero Pets, new content, and more.  We also crowned a new World Champion at the World Finals at Clash Fest. 

But we couldn't have done it without your passion and dedication. From our amazing Content Creators, to our vocal communities, to the Chief who is just starting their journey for the first time, the Clash of Clans game team sends all of you our most heartfelt thank you for being one of the greatest gaming communities ever. We're proud of what we accomplished this year and we can't wait to show you what we've got in store for you in 2023...and beyond!

Clash on!

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. http://supr.cl/ThisArmy

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
http://www.supercell.net/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent’s Guide:
http://www.supercell.net/parents

snippet.title: We Grow Organic Fruits And Vegetables - 100% Healthy
snippet.description:
In this video we try to do organic farming. We try to grow vegetables and fruits in the most organic and natural way possible. In this farming we will not use any kind of pesticides or chemicals to grow any vegetables and fruits.
Lets see how many difficulties we will face in this experiment.
This project will take almost 6 months to complete. This is part-1 of organic farming.
Jai Jawaan Jai Kisaan.

snippet.title: Heeraben Modi Passes Away: PM Modi की मां हीराबेन नहीं रहीं, परिवार में अब कौन-कौन | वनइंडिया हिंदी
snippet.description:
(Heeraben Modi)  (Heeraben Passes Away) (Heeraben Modi Passes Away) (Heeraben Modi Passed Away) (Heeraben Passed Away) (Heeraben Modi Cremation) (PM Modi Family Tree) (Narendra Modi Family) (PM Modi Family Members) (Narendra Modi Brothers) (PM Modi Brothers) (Heeraben Modi Biography) (Heeraben Modi Life Journey) (Heeraben Modi Life Story) (Heeraben Modi Profile) (Heeraben Modi No More) (Heeraben Modi death) (Heeraben Modi Last Will) (Heeraben) (Hiraben Modi) (Hiraben death) (Hiraba Death) (Narendra Modi) (PM Modi Mother) (PM Modi Mother Heeraben) (Ahmedabad)  (UN Mehta Hospital) मां... जिनका होना ही एक छत्र छांव का अहसास करवाया करता था, जिनसे मिलकर प्रधानमंत्री नरेंद्र मोदी को ममता और स्नेह का अहसास हुआ करता था... वो मां हाराबेन पंच तत्व में विलीन हो गई हैं। सौ वर्ष की आयु में उन्होंने अपनी अंतिम सांस ली। उनकी अंतिम क्रिया में प्रधानमंत्री मोदी का पूरा परिवार एक साथ दिखाई दिया। इनके सभी भाई मां की अंतिम यात्रा में शामिल हुए., और उन्हें नम आंखों से अंतिम विदाई दी। (Heeraben Modi Age) (Heeraben Modi Date of Birth) (Heeraben Modi Life Story) (Heeraben Modi Profile) (Heeraben Modi Family) (Heeraben Modi Son) (Hiraben Modi) (Heeraben Struggle) प्रधानमंत्री नरेंद्र मोदी की मां इनके परिवार की संरक्षिका के समान थीं। हीराबेन मोदी की छह संतानें हैं। इनके पति दामोदरदास मूलचंद मोदी का निधन पहले ही हो चुका है। पहले पिता और अब मां के गुज़र जाने के बाद प्रधानमंत्री मोदी के परिवार (PM Modi Family) में अब इनके चार भाई और एक बहन हैं (PM Modi Brothers and Sister)। (PM Narendra Modi Mother Heeraben) (Narendra Modi Mother) (Narendra Modi Mother Heeraben) (Damodar Das Mulchand Modi) (Gujarat)

(Heeraben Modi)  (Heeraben Passes Away) (Heeraben Modi Passes Away) (Heeraben Modi Passed Away) (Heeraben Passed Away) (Heeraben Modi Cremation) (PM Modi Family Tree) (Narendra Modi Family) (PM Modi Family Members) (Narendra Modi Brothers) (PM Modi Brothers) (Heeraben Modi Biography) (Heeraben Modi Life Journey) (Heeraben Modi Life Story) (Heeraben Modi Profile) (Heeraben Modi No More) (Heeraben Modi death) (Heeraben Modi Last Will) (Heeraben) (Hiraben Modi) (Hiraben death) (Hiraba Death) (Narendra Modi) (PM Modi Mother) (PM Modi Mother Heeraben) (Ahmedabad)  (UN Mehta Hospital) मां... जिनका होना ही एक छत्र छांव का अहसास करवाया करता था, जिनसे मिलकर प्रधानमंत्री नरेंद्र मोदी को ममता और स्नेह का अहसास हुआ करता था... वो मां हाराबेन पंच तत्व में विलीन हो गई हैं। सौ वर्ष की आयु में उन्होंने अपनी अंतिम सांस ली। उनकी अंतिम क्रिया में प्रधानमंत्री मोदी का पूरा परिवार एक साथ दिखाई दिया। इनके सभी भाई मां की अंतिम यात्रा में शामिल हुए., और उन्हें नम आंखों से अंतिम विदाई दी। (Heeraben Modi Age) (Heeraben Modi Date of Birth) (Heeraben Modi Life Story) (Heeraben Modi Profile) (Heeraben Modi Family) (Heeraben Modi Son) (Hiraben Modi) (Heeraben Struggle) प्रधानमंत्री नरेंद्र मोदी की मां इनके परिवार की संरक्षिका के समान थीं। हीराबेन मोदी की छह संतानें हैं। इनके पति दामोदरदास मूलचंद मोदी का निधन पहले ही हो चुका है। पहले पिता और अब मां के गुज़र जाने के बाद प्रधानमंत्री मोदी के परिवार (PM Modi Family) में अब इनके चार भाई और एक बहन हैं (PM Modi Brothers and Sister)। (PM Narendra Modi Mother Heeraben) (Narendra Modi Mother) (Narendra Modi Mother Heeraben) (Damodar Das Mulchand Modi) (Gujarat)

snippet.title: The Brawlies 2022 - Brawl Stars Community Award Show!
snippet.description:
Download NOW!! ►► https://supr.cl/2K62CZG
Be a BRAWLER! Subscribe! ►► https://supr.cl/subscribe

#TheBrawlies #brawlstars 

An epic battle royale made for mobile! Play with friends or solo across a variety of game modes in under three minutes.

Unlock and upgrade dozens of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Collect unique skins to stand out and show off. Battle in a variety of mysterious locations within the Brawliverse!

BATTLE IN MULTIPLE GAME MODES
- Gem Grab (3v3): Team up and out-strategize the opposing team. Collect and hold 10 gems to win, but get fragged and lose your gems.
- Showdown (Solo/Duo): A battle royale style fight for survival. Collect power ups for your Brawler. Grab a friend or play solo - be the last Brawler standing in the rowdiest battle royale yet. Winner take all!
- Brawl Ball (3v3): It's a whole new Brawl game! Show off your soccer/football skills and score two goals before the other team. There are no red cards here.
- Bounty (3v3): Take out opponents to earn stars, but don’t let them pick you off. The squad with the most stars wins the match!
- Heist (3v3): Protect your team’s safe and try to crack open your opponents’. Navigate the map to sneak, blast and blow your way clear to the enemies treasure.
- Special Events: Limited time special PvE and PvP game modes.
- Championship Challenge: Join Brawl Stars' esports scene with in-game qualifiers!

UNLOCK AND UPGRADE BRAWLERS
Collect and upgrade a variety of Brawlers with powerful Super abilities, Star Powers and Gadgets! Level them up and collect unique skins.

BRAWL PASS
Complete quests, open Brawl Boxes, earn Gems, pins and an exclusive Brawl Pass skin! Fresh content every season.

BECOME THE STAR PLAYER
Climb the local and regional leaderboards to prove you’re the greatest Brawler of them all!

CONSTANTLY EVOLVING
Look out for new Brawlers, skins, maps, special events and games modes in the future.

PLEASE NOTE! Brawl Stars is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 9 years of age to play or download Brawl Stars.

Features:
- Team up for real-time 3v3 battles against players from across the world
- A fast-paced multiplayer battle royale mode made for mobile
- Unlock and collect new, powerful Brawlers - each with a signature attack and Super ability
- New events and game modes daily
- Battle solo or with friends
- Climb to the top of the leaderboards in global and local rankings 
- Join or start your own Club with fellow players to share tips and battle together
- Customize Brawlers with unlockable skins
- Player-designed maps offer challenging new terrain to master

From the makers of Clash of Clans, Clash Royale and Boom Beach!

Support:
Contact us in-game via Settings, Help and Support — or visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/brawl-stars/

Privacy Policy:
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
http://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

http://supercell.com/en/parents/

Teri Bataan Pe Jo Hansgi Mein Eb To Pakka Fasgi Mein
Le Hath Diya Tere Hatha Me Eb Kade Na Jau Dur Oh Yaraa
Rani Ho Tera Laya Me Laya Me Hai Lal Sharara
Naina Te Tane Marya Yo Marya Yo Kisa Teer Yo Marya
Mere Dada Dadi Wait Kare Kab Bahu Chore Ki Avegi 
Desi Ghee Ka Tatha Churma Hatha Te Khuwavegi 
Re Sare Jhoothe Wade Tere Thik Na Irade Tere
Chail Chora Haryane Ka Tu Lage Se Hai Ghana Payara
Rani Ho Tera Laya Me Laya Me Hai Lal Sharara
Naina Te Tane Marya Yo Marya Yo Kisa Teer Yo Marya
Piya Ji Mera Layaya Ho Layaya Ho Hai Laal Sharara
Naina Te Mane Marya Yo Marya Yo Kisa Teer Yo Marya

रॉनी हो तेरा ल्याया में
ल्याया में हाय लाल शरारा
नैना ते तने मारया यो मारया यो किसा तीर यो मारया
तेरी गोलमोल ये बातें जानू , मानु ना में ये कदे ना मानु
हद से सोनी नार तेरी मने तेरे खातिर रूप संवारा
रॉनी हो तेरा ल्याया में
ल्याया में हाय लाल शरारा
नैना ते तने मारया यो मारया यो किसा तीर यो मारया
तू हुक़्क़ुम तो कर सरकार मेरी कदमा में चाँद में धर दयुन्गा
या ज़िन्दगी तेरे नाम करि तेरी खातिर तो में मर जयुंगा
ना दिल का ओपन गेट करूँ छोरे में तने हेट करूँ
ना चाइये कोई चाँद मने और ना चाइये कोई मने सितारा
रॉनी हो तेरा ल्याया में
ल्याया में हाय लाल शरारा
नैना ते तने मारया यो मारया यो किसा तीर यो मारया
तू राधा मेरी में श्याम तेरा या जोड़ी ना पावै ज़माने में
सर नेम मेरा इब वेट करे तेरे नाम के पाछे आने में
तेरी बातां पे जो हस्स गी में हाय इब तोह पक्का फस गी में
ले हाथ दिया तेरी हाथा में इब कदे ना जाऊ दूर ओ यारा
रॉनी हो तेरा ल्याया में
ल्याया में हाय लाल शरारा
नैना ते तने मारया यो मारया यो किसा तीर यो मारया
मेरे दादा दादी वेट करें क़द बहू छोरे की आवाएगी
देसी घी का ताता चूरमा हाथा ते खुवावगी
रे सारे जूठे वादे रे तेरे ठीक ना इरादे तेरे
तू चैल छोरा हरियाणे का लागे सें घना प्यारा
रॉनी हो तेरा ल्याया में
ल्याया में हाय लाल शरारा
नैना ते तने मारया यो मारया यो किसा तीर यो मारया
पिया जी मेरा ल्याया हो ल्याया हो
हाय लाल शरारा
नैना ते मने मारया हो मारया हो किसा तीर यो मारया

#NainaKeTeer #RenukaPanwar #HaryanviSong
